    \n                 \n                               \n                   \n                     Miramar Beach \n                                                                                       \n                           Emeril's Coastal \n                                                       icon--reservations Reserve \n                                                   \n                                                             \n                 \n                               \n                   \n                     Las Vegas \n                                                                                       \n                           Emeril's New Orleans Fish House \n                                                       icon--reservations Reserve \n                                                   \n                                               \n                           Delmonico Steakhouse \n                                                       icon--reservations Reserve \n                                                   \n                                                             \n                 \n                           \n           \n \n               About Emeril \n             \n               Gift Cards \n             \n               Press \n             \n               Careers \n             \n             Restaurants \n \n             \n                               \n                   \n                     New Orleans \n                                                                                       \n                           Emeril's \n                         \n                                               \n                           Meril \n                         \n                                                             \n                 \n                               \n                   \n                     Miramar Beach \n                                                                                       \n                           Emeril's Coastal \n                         \n                                                             \n                 \n                               \n                   \n                     Las Vegas \n                                                                                       \n                           Emeril's New Orleans Fish House \n                         \n                                               \n                           Delmonico Steakhouse \n                         \n                                                             \n                 \n                           \n           \n             About Emeril \n           \n             Gift Cards \n           \n             Press \n           \n             Careers \n           icon--reservations New Orleans \n                 \n                  Meril                 \n               \n                 \n                  Emeril's                 \n               Miramar Beach \n                 \n                  Emeril's Coastal                 \n               Las Vegas \n                 \n                  Delmonico Steakhouse                 \n               \n                 \n                  Emeril's New Orleans Fish House                 \n               Chef Emeril Lagasse owns and operates restaurants in cities nationwide: New Orleans, Las Vegas and Miramar Beach, FL. All of Chef Emeril\u2019s restaurants and teams strive for the best in two pillars of the industry: excellent service and outstanding cuisine. Each restaurant\u2019s menu is unique, created by the chef de cuisine and his team and overseen by Chef Emeril. Our environment is fast-paced, energetic and rewarding, and there\u2019s room for growth within the company. We\u2019re a tight-knit group with excellent benefits, and we encourage creativity \u2014 whether it\u2019s in our cocktails, cuisine, style of service, or back of the house. Persons interested in applying for employment can complete employment applications in person at the restaurant. We hope to hear from you soon. Please see current openings listed below. The most important aspect of our service is the team effort and attitude of working together. This means everyone striving for the same goal and the same standard of excellence. Believing in ourselves and understanding that we want the best for our employees and for our customers is the key to our success. The restaurants of Chef Emeril Lagasse are comprised of people who are dedicated to providing the best possible food, service and ambience to our guests. The self-respect, pride and commitment that all employees possess is what makes our restaurants the successes that they are. Being better than you were the day before and continuing to learn everyday is the foundation that our restaurants are built upon. This foundation is apparent in every aspect of our restaurants; in the depth and layering of the flavor of our food, in personable and sincere service, and in our bold, yet unpretentious, design elements. Personal service and attention to detail is what we're all about. Consistency. Personal service is name recognition and reading your guest to learn what dining experience the guest is anticipating during each visit to our restaurants. Attention to detail is going the extra mile to make sure all guests' needs are met. All of Emeril's restaurants are committed to a policy of equal opportunity in employment for everyone, regardless of race, color, sex, religion, national origin, age, disability, pregnancy, sexual orientation, gender identity or expression, genetic information, veteran status, or any other basis protected by law. We are committed to administering our personnel actions in accordance with applicable laws.\u00a0 This policy applies to all terms and conditions of employment, including hiring, promotion, compensation, discipline, discharge, or other employment decisions. Emeril's restaurants' managers generally are promoted from within the ranks of our employees. Selected employees who are enthusiastic about advancing their careers receive hands-on training in key aspects of management in order to prepare them for possible promotion. Managers in our restaurants are offered challenging and rewarding opportunities. Our management benefits package currently includes: Generous contribution to health, dental, vision and life insurance premiums 100% Company paid long-term disability insurance Paid Time Off (Up to 3 weeks) 401(k) plan Access to Supplemental insurance including: Cancer, Critical Illness, Accident, and Short-term Disability Merchandise and dining discounts Training and development Delmonico Steakhouse is hiring for the following management positions:\r\n Front of House Dining Room Manager Apply in person at Delmonico Steakhouse -  3355 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109  at the Venetian Resort. You may also email your resume to  delmonicosteakhouse.employment@emerillagasse.com 3355 Las Vegas Blvd. South Las Vegas NV, 89109 At Emeril\u2019s we strive to create an environment that attracts and cultivates talent from across the industry.  We are devoted to our customers and our employees. We have high standards and want employees with an enthusiastic sense of hospitality and eagerness to learn and improve every single day. We hold ourselves to the same high standards in creating an atmosphere that promotes and encourages everyone to be the best they can be. As a team we can have fun, work hard and enrich our lives by being of service to others.  \r\n\r\nWe are looking for candidates that have experience in a fast-paced, refined, fine dining atmosphere. Culinary school training is preferred but not required for back of house positions. Candidates must be able to work a flexible schedule including nights, weekends and holidays. Restaurant position benefits package: Health, dental, vision and life insurance program (Comp