ess. The restaurant is also available for restaurant buyouts and partial-buyouts. For more information about booking a private event please email privateparty.ehbno@emerillagasse.com. Private & Semi-Private Dining Options Available \n                   \n                     Info & Floor Plan \n                   \n                   \n                     View \n                   \n                 \n                   \n                     Entrance \n                   \n                   \n                     View \n                   \n                 \n                   \n                     Food Bar \n                   \n                   \n                     View \n                   \n                 \n                   \n                     Tapestry Room \n                   \n                   \n                     View \n                   \n                 Please fill out our Private Dining Request Form Click to view our menus. \u00a9 2023 Emeril's Homebase. All Rights Reserved. \u00a9 2023 Emeril's Homebase. All Rights Reserved.", "size": 67113, "depth": 2, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "emerilsrestaurants.com", "download_latency": 0.1092381477355957, "redirect_times": 2, "redirect_ttl": 18, "redirect_urls": "http://emerilsrestaurants.com/?page_id=386@@https://emerilsrestaurants.com/?page_id=386", "redirect_reasons": "301@@301", "status": 200, "links_url": "https://emerilsrestaurants.com@@https://emerilsrestaurants.com/emerils-new-orleans@@https://www.exploretock.com/emerils-restaurant-new-orleans@@https://emerilsrestaurants.com/meril@@https://www.opentable.com/r/meril-reservations-new-orleans?restref=269761@@https://emerilsrestaurants.com/emerils-coastal@@https://www.opentable.com/r/emerils-coastal-reservations-miramar-beach?restref=444583&lang=en-US&ot_source=Restaurant%20website@@https://emerilsrestaurants.com/emerils-new-orleans-fish-house@@https://www.opentable.com/emerils-new-orleans-fish-house-reservations-las-vegas